{"content": "I need to multiply 418\u2089 \u00d7 658\u2089.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n418\u2089 = 4\u00d79\u00b2 + 1\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070 = 4\u00d781 + 1\u00d79 + 8\u00d71 = 324 + 9 + 8 = 341\u2081\u2080\n\n658\u2089 = 6\u00d79\u00b2 + 5\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070 = 6\u00d781 + 5\u00d79 + 8\u00d71 = 486 + 45 + 8 = 539\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n341 \u00d7 539 = 183,799\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n183799 \u00f7 9 = 20422 r 1\n20422 \u00f7 9 = 2269 r 1\n2269 \u00f7 9 = 252 r 1\n252 \u00f7 9 = 28 r 0\n28 \u00f7 9 = 3 r 1\n3 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 3\n\nReading from bottom to top: **310111\u2089**\n\n310111", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 325}